  {
    "title": "Notes for Junglers",
    "depth": 0,
    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "It is recommended that you play every Jungler at least once to learn their skills, and matchups/recommended equipment builds for different heroes."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "Be aware of invading Roamers/Junglers."
          },
          {
            "text": "Be alert when these heroes are on the enemy team:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "These junglers are weak early game/when at level 1-3."
          },
          {
            "text": "If you use these heroes, be aware of invades from the enemy team:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "(Fanny and Ling are weak until they get Blue Buff.)"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
